colorzero (1.1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Added ability to generate ANSI codes with "format".
  * Added "Color.gradient" method.
  * Exposed the various difference functions in the API ("euclid", "cie1976",
    etc).
  * Various doc fixes and enhancements.

